   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-noquest" image="QN_Npc_Lotus_Elder_Teramai.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>I'm sorry. I'm not being of any help.<BR><BR>
※ <FONT color=#7e12d2>You can get the quest from Terrence Terramai inside the Saint Haven Royal Palace.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-accepting" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-accepting-a" mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>The Prophet?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Okay. I guess we have to search Meteor Crash Site thoroughly.<BR>I'll leave the search to the temple knights so can you go and see the <FONT color=#a82424>Prophet</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-accepting-b" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>What would it be about?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Maybe meeting Velskud last time gave her a shock. Her face remained gloomy from that time onwards. But she suddenly looked for you today. She says she has something to ask you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-accepting-acceptted" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>I got it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Well, I won't say until that.<BR>
You'll know when you see the Prophet.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-1" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Terrence Terramai$<BR>Though she may be the Prophet, she's just a little girl. Sometimes I pity her situation. You may make her better if you talk to her once in a while so go to Royal Palace Underground and meet Rose.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-1" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-1-a" mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>I heard that you have something to ask me.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>You're here....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-1-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-1-b" mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>I was worried about grandpa and Lily so I asked around for news about how they were doing in Prairie Town.... My grandpa's health seems to be failing.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-1-b" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400317">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-1-c" mid="75"><![CDATA[<html>Old vine?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="73"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>I heard that there's a herb that's good for his condition in Lotus Marsh. Could you get some <FONT color=#a82424>old vine</FONT> for me?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-1-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-1-d" mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>Where can I find it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>I know this is not a good time..., But I'm so worried about my grandpa, I can't stand it....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-1-d" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-2" mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rose's face brightens a little)</FONT><BR><FONT color=#a82424>Old vine</FONT> could be easily found in Lotus Marsh in the past. But for some reason, it can only be obtained from the monsters at <FONT color=#a82424>Meteor Crash Site Core</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-2" image="QW_63.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>Please go to <FONT color=#a82424>Meteor Crash Site Core</FONT> and get 3 lumps of <FONT color=#a82424>old vine</FONT>. I think that would be enough to make my grandpa feel better.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-a" mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>A doll?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>Thank you so much. And if I finish making this doll, I'll send the old vine together with this doll.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-a" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-b" mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>It's a present for Lily.<BR>
I think she must be having a hard time because I'm gone.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rose tears up)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-c" mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>I'm not useless even when I don't have the powers.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>I want to go back to Prairie Town right away…, but since I owe my life to Terramai, I need to repay his kindness. And there are people who still need my powers.<BR>
Until they disappear and become useless….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-d" mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>Really?<BR>I always knew that I was different from other people.<BR>
While I was being used by the Black Knight, I wished to be normal. So I hid inside my own self too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-e" mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>But after I met Terramai, I realised that I was being cowardly.<BR>
Terramai told me that I could give strength to many people who were in agony.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-e" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-f" mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>So I'm not going to run away anymore. <BR>
But as I started to accept these powers, ironically they are getting weaker.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rose smiles sadly)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-g" mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>You can always go back if you want to.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>You know....<BR>
If my powers get weaker and weaker and finally disappear, would I be able to go back to Prairie Town?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-g" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-h" mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>It's still dangerous. As long as I have the power, there will be people trying to make use of it. So if I go back to Prairie Town now, I may put the town into danger.<BR>So... when those bad people disappear, or....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-h" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-3-i" mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>Are you okay?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>If all my powers are gone and I become an ordinary girl, I will go back. <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Tears drop from Rose's eyes)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-3-i" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n827_rose-4" mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>I'm sorry to make you listen to all this. I'm just... having a hard time so don't worry.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rose wipes her tears)</FONT><BR>I'll feel better if I cry a little.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n827_rose-4" image="QN_Npc_Lotus_Elder_Teramai.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Rose$<BR>If I find something out, I'll tell you. Right now, I just want to stay alone.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(It'd be better to leave Rose alone for a while. Talk to Terramai)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-4" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-4-a" mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>She seems stronger than before.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Terramai$<BR>Though she may be the Prophet, she's still a little girl.<BR>
I'm proud to see her trying to endure all this with faith.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-4-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-4-b" mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>I think that would be good.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Terramai$<BR>Humans are like that.... If we go through a hardship, we will somehow survive in one way or another.<BR>
I think it'd be better to leave her alone until she feels better.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-4-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-4-c" mid="80"><![CDATA[<html>How about asking help from Cidel?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="79"><![CDATA[<html>$Terramai$<BR>
Then while the Prophet is taking a rest, shall we do our own work?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n822_teramai-4-c" image="QN_Npc_Sidel.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n822_teramai-4-d" mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>Got it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Terramai$<BR>That's a good idea.<BR>Since the temple knights would be unfamiliar with Lotus Marsh, Fairystar members who know this place well would be of great help.<BR>Please go to <FONT color=#a82424>Cidel</FONT> and ask for help.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
